  <brief_title>Do SGAs Improve Identification of the CTM</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does the Insertion of a Supraglottic Airway Device Improve a Clinicans Ability to Correctly Identify the Cricothyroid Membrane?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
