  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, observational, non-interventional study that will examine if the insertion of a
      Supraglottic airway will increase accuracy of identifying the cricothyroid membrane
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients consented, meeting inclusion criteria are assessed by clinicians under GA with and
      without a supraglottic airway in situ. The accuracy of CTM identification by palpation is
      assessed using ultrasound.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
